"{\"uid\": \"rferl.org-a-russia-olympics-world-friendship-games-postponed-33056872.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Share  Share  Print  Russia's World Friendship Games, scheduled for September 2024, have been postponed until 2025, according to a July 30 statement by the International Friendship Association, the official organizer of the games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999992673189537, \"rank\": 7.264932485467606e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The association said \\\"insufficient time for the recovery of leading athletes\\\" from the Paris Olympics prompted the delay.\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Russian authorities and organizers claimed the competition would include athletes from 70 countries around the world who would participate in33 Olympic and non-Olympic sports.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.7472034836376209, \"rank\": 0.3328176809922131, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"non-Olympic sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The games, reminiscent of the 1984 Soviet Union's Friendship Games, have provoked condemnations from the International Olympic Committee and the World Anti-Doping Agency.To read the original story on RFE/RL's Russian Service, clickhere.\", \"fro